title: Ep. 14 - Ted Nivison Gets Revenge
description: IT'S TED TIME BABY! YouTuber and alleged milk man Ted Nivison joins the boys for their second guest episode of the show. Ted talks about his experience with being Down Bad, Slime creates a Jigsaw fart puzzle, and once again the boys complain about the shortcomings of Twitch streamers.
